{
  "stem": "1338.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "His two brothers, among others, went to Russia and actually became-- I don't-- don't want to make this interview a study of the history, but they became actually some very big shots, commissars, in the National Program for Economic Independence, called the NEP, under Lenin.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And-- and they were experts in forestry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And shortly thereafter-- and I remember letters coming home, seldom-- that one of them was sent to Siberia and died there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And one went to Leningrad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that was, I presume, the time when Stalin took over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then just an irony of times that his son became a big shot under Stalin in forestry.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Anyway, my father was in forestry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "This was his business.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He lived in Lodz because he went there and he had a lumber yard.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "First, he had a prosperous life, obviously.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "When I was born, he built a home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Not a separate home in the city, but on top of some of other building.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He had a couple of apartments.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "My mother-- so that's who my father was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "My mother was born in Grodno, which is today also White Russia, and at that time was Russia, obviously.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And she was born one-- her name was [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Grad, ?] family name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Her father was a prominent citizen of the city who, by the way, did it all by himself.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And it was very clear.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He ran away from home from some small town-- I don't remember the name-- became a baker's apprentice.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And eventually, when I saw him, which was age of close to 80, I remember he was very well educated, spoke excellent-- I don't remember his Polish, but his Russian was excellent and Polish probably too.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
